<headline>Severe Thunderstorm Watch issued June 17 at 5:48AM CDT until June 17 at 8:00AM CDT by NWS Saint Louis</headline>
<description>SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WATCH 380 REMAINS VALID UNTIL 8 AM CDT THIS
MORNING FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS
IN ILLINOIS THIS WATCH INCLUDES 9 COUNTIES
IN SOUTH CENTRAL ILLINOIS
BOND                  CLINTON               FAYETTE
MARION                MONTGOMERY            WASHINGTON
IN SOUTHWEST ILLINOIS
MACOUPIN              MADISON               SAINT CLAIR
THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF ALTON, BELLEVILLE, CAHOKIA,
CENTRALIA, EDWARDSVILLE, LITCHFIELD, SALEM, AND VANDALIA.</description>
